\">ℝ</a>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HPow.hPow\">^</a> <span class=\"fn\">2</span>)</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">ψ</span>)</div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QuantumMechanics/OneDimension/HarmonicOscillator/Basic.html#QuantumMechanics.OneDimension.HarmonicOscillator.schrodingerOperator_eq","kind":"theorem","line":151,"name":"QuantumMechanics.OneDimension.HarmonicOscillator.schrodingerOperator_eq","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L151-L158"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">noncomputable def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QuantumMechanics/OneDimension/HarmonicOscillator/Basic.html#QuantumMechanics.OneDimension.HarmonicOscillator.schrodingerOperator\"><span class=\"name\">QuantumMechanics</span>.<span class=\"name\">OneDimension</span>.<span class=\"name\">HarmonicOscillator</span>.<span class=\"name\">schrodingerOperator</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">Q</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QuantumMechanics/OneDimension/HarmonicOscillator/Basic.html#QuantumMechanics.OneDimension.HarmonicOscillator\">HarmonicOscillator</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ψ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a> → <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a> → <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a harmonic oscillator, the Schrodinger Operator corresponding to it\nis defined as the function from `ℝ → ℂ` to `ℝ → ℂ` taking\n\n`ψ ↦ - ℏ^2 / (2 * m) * ψ'' + 1/2 * m * ω^2 * x^2 * ψ`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Q